				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Top 10 Bard Issues (for Tremelo)<a name="49815"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 2 04 6:55 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Those are my 2 of my top 3 issues also.
<br />

<br />
<b>Song pulses / song drops</b> - I even notice the bard song drop bug when I am twisting only 3 songs at raids, let alone 4 songs while single grouped.
<br />

<br />
<b>Bard fizzles rates</b> - I think 5% is still too high given the very nature of how quickly we turn over songs.  It should be down in the 2-3% range.  I miss SOOOO much of the game because I am constantly watching my song window for 1) missed notes, 2) you haven't recovered yet, 3) bash interrupts messages every 2-3 seconds.
<br />

<br />
I have begun to notice I think that there is a lag in even getting told I have missed a note.  Sometimes I swear my casting bar has gone down 0.5 seconds before I see the dreaded red message
<br />

<br />
<b>DX9</b> - The ability to keep 4 songs up at a 95% or better rate has really hurt by the DX9 patch (this is outside of fizzles or the drop bug).  I am not sure exactly why though.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
